OL,3,C'Excessive waste bothers me' - The pub
OL,4,Ccharging customers for leaving food
OL,6,FA couple who came to the pub and ended
OL,7,Fup being charged said they had "never
OL,8,Fheard" of such a policy before.
OL,10,FVerity Farmer took her grievances to
OL,11,Fthe Newest Newquay Facebook group, and
OL,12,Fwrote: "Just been for a Sunday carvery
OL,13,Fat the Star Inn, Vogue, St Day, we
OL,14,Fpaid for our meal at #12 each, and
OL,15,Fwhen we got our bill it had got an
OL,16,Fextra #4.80 added when questioned
OL,17,Fabout it they said it was a charge for
OL,18,Fnot eating all our meal.
OL,20,F"I've never heard anything like that
OL,21,Fbefore."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
