OL,3,C'Excessive waste bothers me' - The pub
OL,4,Ccharging customers for leaving food
OL,6,FBut Mark Graham has said the charge is
OL,7,Fnot to make money, but to cut down on
OL,8,Ffood waste.
OL,10,FHe said: "I don't care about a couple
OL,11,Fof potatoes getting left. It's just
OL,12,Fstupid, excessive waste that bothers
OL,13,Fme. If everyone did that I'd have to
OL,14,Fcook shed loads of food.
OL,16,F"You can take as much as you like,
OL,17,Fcome back as many times as you like
OL,18,Fand as the old Navy saying goes, you
OL,19,Fcan fill your boots. Do whatever you
OL,20,Fwant, just don't waste it."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
