OL,3,C'Excessive waste bothers me' - The pub
OL,4,Ccharging customers for leaving food
OL,6,FHe explained that the extra charge
OL,7,Fcontributes towards the cost of raw
OL,8,Fmaterials but doesn't cover expenses
OL,9,Ffor equipment or staff wages.
OL,11,F"I tell everyone, I'm in this game to
OL,12,Fearn a living, not make a fortune," he
OL,13,Fadded. "
OL,15,FI just like the job. I've always been
OL,16,Fin and out of this job since I was 14
OL,17,Fand it's a way of life. I enjoy it.
OL,18,FI'm making a living, not a killing and
OL,19,FI'm not ripping people off. We want to
OL,20,Fhelp everybody out."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
