OL,3,C'Excessive waste bothers me' - The pub
OL,4,Ccharging customers for leaving food
OL,6,FThe pub has received a lot of support
OL,7,Fonline for it's policy, while staff
OL,8,Fposted a photo of the amount of food
OL,9,Fleft by the couple complaining.
OL,11,FWendy Ann commented: "Never heard of
OL,12,Fthis policy before but what a great
OL,13,Fidea and clearly this is a ridiculous
OL,14,Famount of food to waste and I think
OL,15,Fnot charging for children is
OL,16,Fbrilliant. Great response to the
OL,17,Fposter and shows how you were fully
OL,18,Fjustified."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
