OL,3,C'Excessive waste bothers me' - The pub
OL,4,Ccharging customers for leaving food
OL,6,FHazel Petrie reflected: "As my mum
OL,7,Fwould have said they had eyes bigger
OL,8,Fthan their belly. I hate to see good
OL,9,Ffood wasted. The notice in the Star
OL,10,FInn is clear enough; I've seen it
OL,11,Fmyself. It says you can go back for
OL,12,Fmore so it's perfectly fair."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
