OL,3,C'Excessive waste bothers me' - The pub
OL,4,Ccharging customers for leaving food
OL,6,FJaz Holmes added: "Brilliant idea. We
OL,7,Fwent to a carvery today and saw a
OL,8,Fwoman pile on 10 roast potatoes. No
OL,9,Fexaggeration. I commented to my
OL,10,Fpartner what an absolute waste that's
OL,11,Fgoing to be. If you're able to go up
OL,12,Fas many times as you like then there
OL,13,Fshould be absolutely no waste. Take a
OL,14,Fsmall plate and go and get more if
OL,15,Fneeded. Simples!"
OL,17,FThe original customer's post received
OL,18,Fmore than 400 comments, while The Star
OL,19,FInn itself also weighed in.
