OL,3,C'Excessive waste bothers me' - The pub
OL,4,Ccharging customers for leaving food
OL,6,F"We just try and make sure there is
OL,7,Fenough food for everyone," staff wrote.
OL,9,F"I'm sure if you were a customer later
OL,10,Fon in the day and I had to tell you I
OL,11,Fhad no food left for your booking
OL,12,Fbecause it had all been wasted and
OL,13,Fgone in the bin you would not be very
OL,14,Fhappy and would have made another
OL,15,Fsocial media post too."
